{"word":"ὄψ 1","slug":"ὄψ 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n76280\" key=\"o)/y1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὄψ</orth> (A), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, poetic Noun, used in obliq. cases of sg., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀπός, ὀπί, ὄπα</foreign>, <sense id=\"n76280.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">voice</tr_>, whether in speaking, shouting, lamenting, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ἀτρείδεω ὀπὸς ἔκλυον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:76\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.76</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:150\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.150</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:222\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.222</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:451\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.451</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; or in singing, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Κίρκης . . ἀειδούσης ὀπὶ καλῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:221\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.221</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:61\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.61</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἄειδον ἀμειβόμεναι ὀπὶ καλῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:604\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.604</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope></bibl>, al., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg003.perseus-grc1:7:84\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.84</biblScope></bibl>, al., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0199.tlg002:16:129\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.129</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg001.perseus-grc1:60\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Supp.\">Supp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">60</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.), etc.; also of cicadae, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄπα λειριόεσσαν ἱεῖσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:152\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.152</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of lambs, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀκούουσαι ὄπα ἀρνῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:435\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.435</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of flutes, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αὐλῶν φθεγγομένων ἱμερόεσσαν ὄπα</quote_> <bibl n=\"Thgn. 532\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thgn.\">Thgn.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">532</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n76280.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">word</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὡς γὰρ ἐγὼν ὄπ᾽ ἄκουσα θεῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.53</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀμείλικτον δ᾽ ὄπ᾽ ἄκουσαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:137\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.137</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:98\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.98</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1068\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1068</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.), etc. (Cogn. with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔπος, εἰπεῖν</foreign>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}